description: Stunning two Bedroom two Bathroom corner unit at exclusive Twenty Two Liberty! This sun-splashed home boasts 10 foot ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows with beautiful views of the city and harbor. Unit features include private balcony, hardwood floors, custom closets, motorized window shades, and abundant closet space. The kitchen is meticulously appointed with top of the line appliances by Wolf, Miele, and Subzero. Both bedrooms are generous in size and the primary bedroom captures gorgeous views of the Harbor. En suite primary bathroom boasts Italian marble, soaking tub, glass shower, and double vanity. Twenty Two Liberty offers unparalleled amenities, including 24-hour concierge, a magnificent clubroom with a terrace overlooking the harbor, fitness center, and conference room. Includes 1 Deeded parking space and additional storage.
